{"content": "I need to multiply 602 \u00d7 435 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 602\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 0 + 2 = 486 + 0 + 2 = 488\u2081\u2080\n- 435\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 5 = 324 + 27 + 5 = 356\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 488 \u00d7 356 = 173,728\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 173728 \u00f7 9 = 19303 r 1\n- 19303 \u00f7 9 = 2144 r 7\n- 2144 \u00f7 9 = 238 r 2\n- 238 \u00f7 9 = 26 r 4\n- 26 \u00f7 9 = 2 r 8\n- 2 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 2\n\nReading from bottom to top: **284271\u2089**\n\n284271", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 338}